#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Modularity SPI reference"
msgstr "模块化 SPI 参考"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-experimental\" title=\"This extension requests early feedback to mature the idea\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">experimental</a>"
msgstr "<a class=\"status-label status-experimental\" title=\"此扩展程序希望征集早期反馈以完善该想法\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">实验性</a>"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This document describes the build items that extension authors use to integrate with the xref:modularity.adoc[Quarkus modularity] system.\n"
"Extensions can declare boot modules, add inter-module dependencies, and consume the completed module model."
msgstr "本文档介绍了扩展作者用于与 xref:modularity.adoc[Quarkus 模块化] 系统集成的构建项。扩展可以声明启动模块、添加模块间依赖关系，并使用已完成的模块模型。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`BootModulePathBuildItem`"
msgstr "`BootModulePathBuildItem`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`BootModulePathBuildItem` is a `MultiBuildItem` produced by extensions.\n"
"It declares that a named module must be placed on the boot module path."
msgstr "`BootModulePathBuildItem` 是由扩展生成的 `MultiBuildItem` 。它声明必须将一个指定名称的模块放置在启动模块路径上。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"An extension should produce this item when it provides a module that must be in the JDK's boot module layer.\n"
"This is necessary when the module is required before the dynamic module loader (`smallrye-modules`) starts, or when the module must participate in the boot class loading chain."
msgstr "当扩展提供了一个必须位于 JDK 启动模块层中的模块时，应生成此项。当该模块需要在动态模块加载器（ `smallrye-modules` ）启动之前被调用，或者该模块必须参与启动类加载链时，此操作是必要的。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The constructor takes a single `String` parameter: the module name."
msgstr "该构造函数接受一个 `String` 类型的参数：模块名称。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The modularity extension computes the transitive closure of all declared boot modules.\n"
"If a boot module depends on other modules (via `LINKED` dependencies), those modules are also included in the boot set automatically.\n"
"Automatic modules are excluded from the boot set because they cannot be linked by `jlink`."
msgstr "模块化扩展会计算所有已声明的启动模块的传递闭包。如果某个启动模块依赖于其他模块（通过 `LINKED` 依赖关系），这些模块也会自动被纳入启动集。自动生成的模块不会被纳入启动集，因为 `jlink` 无法对其进行链接。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`AddDependencyBuildItem`"
msgstr "`AddDependencyBuildItem`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`AddDependencyBuildItem` is a `MultiBuildItem` produced by extensions.\n"
"It adds a dependency between two modules at build time."
msgstr "`AddDependencyBuildItem` 是由扩展生成的 `MultiBuildItem` 。它在构建时在两个模块之间建立依赖关系。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"An extension should produce this item when it needs to wire a module dependency that is not expressed in the Maven POM or in the module's `module-info.class` descriptor.\n"
"This is common when Quarkus extensions generate code that references types from another module, or when service loading relationships must be declared explicitly."
msgstr "当扩展需要连接 Maven POM 或模块的 `module-info.class` 描述符中未明确指定的模块依赖时，应生成此项。这种情况常见于 Quarkus 扩展生成引用了其他模块中类型的代码时，或者必须显式声明服务加载关系时。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The constructor takes three parameters: the source module name (`String`), the target module name (`String`), and a set of dependency modifiers (`Modifiers<Dependency.Modifier>`)."
msgstr "该构造函数接受三个参数：源模块名称（ `String` ）、目标模块名称（ `String` ）以及一组依赖修饰符（ `Modifiers<Dependency.Modifier>` ）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When multiple items declare the same source/target pair, their modifier sets are merged."
msgstr "当多个项声明了相同的源/目标对时，它们的修饰符集将被合并。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`ApplicationModuleInfoBuildItem`"
msgstr "`ApplicationModuleInfoBuildItem`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`ApplicationModuleInfoBuildItem` is a `SimpleBuildItem` produced by the modularity extension.\n"
"It contains the completed `AppModuleModel`, which includes the module descriptor for every module in the application, the set of boot modules, and the set of JDK modules in use."
msgstr "`ApplicationModuleInfoBuildItem` 是由模块化扩展生成的 `SimpleBuildItem` 。它包含已完成的 `AppModuleModel` ，其中包含应用程序中每个模块的模块描述符、启动模块集以及正在使用的 JDK 模块集。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This item is consumed by downstream packaging extensions such as the xref:jlink.adoc[jlink extension].\n"
"Extension authors generally do not need to consume this item unless they are implementing a custom packaging step."
msgstr "该项由下游打包扩展（如 xref:jlink.adoc[jlink 扩展] ）使用。除非扩展作者正在实现自定义打包步骤，否则通常无需使用该项。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Dependency modifiers"
msgstr "依赖修饰符"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `Dependency.Modifier` enum (from `io.smallrye.modules.desc`) defines the following values.\n"
"These are used with `AddDependencyBuildItem` to control how the dependency is wired."
msgstr "`Dependency.Modifier` 枚举（来自 `io.smallrye.modules.desc` ）定义了以下值。这些值与 `AddDependencyBuildItem` 配合使用，用于控制依赖项的连接方式。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`LINKED`"
msgstr "`链接`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The dependency is linked for class loading.\n"
"Classes from the target module are visible to the source module's class loader."
msgstr "该依赖关系是为类加载而建立的。源模块的类加载器可以访问目标模块中的类。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`READ`"
msgstr "`阅读`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The dependency is readable from the source module.\n"
"Exported packages from the target module are accessible to the source module."
msgstr "源模块可以读取该依赖项。源模块可以访问目标模块导出的包。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`SERVICES`"
msgstr "`服务`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Service implementations in the target module are available to the source module via `ServiceLoader`."
msgstr "源模块可通过 `ServiceLoader` 访问目标模块中的服务实现。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`OPTIONAL`"
msgstr "`可选`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The dependency is optional.\n"
"If the target module is not present at link time, the dependency is silently ignored rather than causing a failure."
msgstr "该依赖项是可选的。如果在链接时目标模块不存在，该依赖项将被静默忽略，而不会导致链接失败。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`TRANSITIVE`"
msgstr "`及物`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The dependency is transitive.\n"
"Any module that depends on the source module also implicitly depends on the target module."
msgstr "该依赖关系具有传递性。任何依赖于源模块的模块，也隐式地依赖于目标模块。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`SYNTHETIC`"
msgstr "`SYNTHETIC`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The dependency was added by a framework rather than declared in the original module descriptor. _Note:_ because modifier sets are merged when a dependency is declared in two places, this modifier would take precedence over a non-synthetic dependency, which is a minor detail but possibly undesirable. Thus, this modifier may change to be \"non-synthetic\" or something along those lines in the final version, so that an explicit dependency will never be marked as being synthetic."
msgstr "该依赖关系是由框架添加的，而非在原始模块描述符中声明的。 _注意：_ 由于在两个位置声明依赖关系时修饰符集会被合并，因此该修饰符将优先于非合成依赖关系——这虽是个细微之处，但可能并非预期结果。 因此，在最终版本中，该修饰符可能会改为“非合成”或类似表述，以确保显式依赖关系绝不会被标记为合成依赖。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`MANDATED`"
msgstr "`强制性`"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The dependency is mandated by specification (for example, the implicit dependency on `java.base`)."
msgstr "该依赖关系由规范强制要求（例如，对 `java.base` 的隐式依赖）。"

#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Related core build items"
msgstr "相关核心出装"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The `quarkus-core-deployment` module provides two additional build items that affect the module graph.\n"
"These are documented separately but are noted here for completeness."
msgstr "`quarkus-core-deployment` 模块提供了两个额外的构建项，这些项会影响模块图。虽然这些内容已在其他文档中单独说明，但为确保完整性，在此一并提及。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/main/guides/modularity-reference.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`ModuleOpenBuildItem` declares that one module should open specified packages to another module (equivalent to the `--add-opens` JVM flag).\n"
"`ModuleEnableNativeAccessBuildItem` declares that a module requires native access (equivalent to the `--enable-native-access` JVM flag)."
msgstr "`ModuleOpenBuildItem` 声明某个模块应向另一个模块开放指定的包（相当于 JVM 标志 `--add-opens` ）。 `ModuleEnableNativeAccessBuildItem` 声明某个模块需要本机访问权限（相当于 JVM 标志 `--enable-native-access` ）。"
